sequenceDiagram
    participant U as User (HR-200)
    participant RC as Route Context
    participant TAK as TAK Kernel
    participant AI as Inference Provider
    participant T as Tool Handler
    participant DB as Audit DB

    U->>RC: Navigate to /ops
    RC-->>TAK: domain tools, sensitivity, agent ID

    U->>TAK: "Create backlog item for login bug"
    TAK->>TAK: Filter tools by role + agent grants
    TAK->>TAK: Assemble system prompt + directives

    TAK->>AI: Messages + filtered tools
    AI-->>TAK: tool_call: create_backlog_item

    TAK->>TAK: Check execution mode = proposal
    TAK-->>U: Approval card (tool, params, rationale)

    U->>TAK: Approve

    TAK->>T: Execute create_backlog_item
    T-->>TAK: Result: BLI-00123 created

    par Audit Recording
        TAK->>DB: ToolExecution record
        TAK->>DB: AgentActionProposal -> executed
        TAK->>DB: AuthorizationDecisionLog -> allow
        TAK->>DB: TokenUsage record
    end

    TAK-->>U: "Created BLI-00123: Fix login bug"
